as district of Madhya Pradesh; and solar power plant with an installed capacity of 5MW in Maharashtra and 5.5MW in Madhya Pradesh, as well as 10 mines located in Maharashtra and Madhya Pradesh. The company was formerly known as Manganese Ore (India) Limited. and changed its name to MOIL Limited in 2010. MOIL Limited was founded in 1896 and is based in Nagpur, India."}}